\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Similarly, SAM is a stuffed dolphin that engages NDD children in a variety
 of play tasks.
 Sam’s affordances and behavior has been designed for this specific target
 group in cooperation with a team of therapists from SAM Foundation and
 L’Abilità, two non-profit institution in Netherlands and Italy respectively.
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Sam"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


