\begin_layout Standard
Still, given the wide range of NDD conditions and the specfic characteristics
 of each single subject, there is space for new exploratory experiences
 involving robotic interaction to enlarge the set of success stories and
 identify new forms of therapeutic and educational interventions for this
 target group.
\end_layout

